DOC.brief_summary: The aim of this study is to compare different FSH/LH ratios in controlled ovarian stimulation
DOC.brief_title: Influence of FSH/LH Ratio in Controlled Ovarian Stimulation
DOC.criteria: Patients undergoing IVF cycles in Cruces University Hospital. Signed IVF and cryopreservation informed consent. Age >35 and <40 years. FSH levels <10 mIU/ml. When inclusion criteria are not fulfilled
